works.description: With an aim to increase the brand’s exclusivity and give a stiff competition to BMW, German automaker Audi is rolling out special editions in markets around the world. The Volkswagen unit will start selling the special edition two-tone exterior turbo-diesel V-12-powered Audi Q7 in Russia next month, with prices starting at €200,000 ($285,000). The Q7 Special Edition SUV is going to cost the Audi lovers almost twice the base price for a Q7 in Russia. In June, Audi will roll out the special edition R8 V-10 Pure Sport in the United Arab Emirates,
